query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-volley',
'asp.net-ajax',
'average',
'botframework',
'casperjs',
'frontend',
'graphql',
'mingw',
'out-of-memory',
'pivot',
'routes',
'ruby-on-rails-3.1',
'signalr',
'spring-mvc',
'views');
